snippet.title: STARL /Warp Nexus Space Metaverse and MMO Game Tour on Discord #UnrealEngine5  #MMOGames
snippet.description:
The STARL Team hosted a Livestream metaverse and Warp Nexus in-game tour on Discord packed with reveals, updates, and details. If you missed it, check out the video, and chapters marked below.

Hosted by:
Metaverse/game lead developer Scott Brown
Project concept creator, Moe Larson 
Project manager, Johnny Utah

**Video compliments of STARL team member, Obie Zeard: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDRccEftHWW3Qu1NK9oM_lA

CHAPTERS:
00:00 - Intro
01:46 - Starting Area
02:30 - The Hub
02:54 - Living Modules https://opensea.io/collection/living-...

05:37 - STARLcade Minigame Arcade

08:22 - Ship Customization
09:08 - Group Meditation Dome

30:11 - Mycenans Station

30:28 - Mycenans Station Marketplace and Playloop
31:06 - Buy, Sell, and Build Inventory

38:15 - Create Single Player Mission: Courier to The Atmos
39:15 - Create Single Player Mission: Mining to The Seymonians
40:15 - Mining Ore

43:00 - Mission Difficulty
44:42 - Community Talk
